://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B4%D9%90%D9%84%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fail"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lose heart, to despair"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to foil, to thwart, to frustrate"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"failure","examples":[{"text":"لفت السياسي نديم الجابري اليوم الجمعة الى ان الخلافات واضحة في التحالف الشيعي ابرزها عملية تسجيل التحالفات لخوض الانتخابات المقبلة ، معتبرا انه لا توجد رؤية مشتركة لمكونات التحالف الوطني بشأن القضايا الوطنية والانشقاقات في الكتل السياسية ناتجة عن فشلها الذريع.","english":"The politician nadīm al-jabrī has on Friday drawn attention to the patent disagreements in the Shia alliance, most notably the alliances for the campaign for the election of the coming year, judging that there is no common vision about the constituents of the national alliance over the national affairs and the splits in the political blocs arising from their abject failure."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"disappointment, letdown, flop, dud, fiasco"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of فَشِلَ (fašila) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"failed, unsuccessful, futile, vain, fruitless"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"faint-hearted, cowardly, craven, chicken"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33932","headword_ar":"فَشِلَ","root":"f$l","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb, K,) aor"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fa$alN","text_ar":"فَشَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, Msb;) a verb of which exs. occur in the Kur iii. 118 and viii. 48; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fa$ala","text_ar":"فَشَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fa$ala","text_ar":"فَشَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; two dial. vars., the former of these agreeable with a reading of the latter verse of the Kur-án, and the latter agreeable with a reading of the same verse by El- Hasan El-Basree; (O;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, cowardly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak-hearted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flagging, remiss,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"languid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"timorous."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fa$alato","text_ar":"فَشَلَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fa$alato mifo$alahaA","text_ar":"فَشَلَتْ مِفْشَلَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fa$alato fi$olahaA","text_ar":"فَشَلَتْ فِشْلَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, * TA, [in the CK ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fa$~alatohu","text_ar":"فَشَّلَتْهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", the pronoun relating to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfi$ol","text_ar":"الفِشْل"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fa$olN","text_ar":"فَشْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aifota$alatohu","text_ar":"اِفْتَشَلَتْهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K, * TA,) thus accord. to the M as well as the O, (TA,) i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mifo$alahaA","text_ar":"مِفْشَلَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fi$olahaA","text_ar":"فِشْلَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) [in the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aifota$alato","text_ar":"اِفْتَشَلَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone, i. e. without any complement, as though it were intrans.; or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Af$lt","text_ar":"افشلت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is said in the TA to be the reading in the copies of the K, but which I have not found in any;] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tf$~lt","text_ar":"تفشّلت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[mentioned without any complement, as though intrans.]; (K, TA;) said of a woman, (O, K, TA,) in relation to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fi$ol","text_ar":"فِشْل"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which is also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mifo$al","text_ar":"مِفْشَل"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, O,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She hung a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vawob","text_ar":"ثَوْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (thus in the O, in the TA"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"her"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vwb","text_ar":"ثوب"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"camel-vehicle called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hawodaj","text_ar":"هَوْدَج"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"then put it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drew it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the main part thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"within it, and bound its extremities to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawaAEid","text_ar":"قَوَاعِد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"four pieces of wood that form a square frame upon which it is fixed"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see its sing."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAEidapN","text_ar":"قَاعِدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")]; this being [beneath her (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fi$olN","text_ar":"فِشْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":") so as to be to her] a preservative from the heads of the [curved pieces of wood called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHonaA='","text_ar":"اَحْنَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HinowN","text_ar":"حِنْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"q. v.] and the [apparatus called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqotaAb","text_ar":"اَقْتَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qitobN","text_ar":"قِتْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"q. v.] and the knots of the cord called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuSom","text_ar":"عُصْم"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiSaAmN","text_ar":"عِصَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"q. v.]: (O, TA:) so says ISh. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","TA","IAar"]}]}}